name: Espolex® WT361
description:
Espolex® WT361 is a thermoplastic elastomer with low die drool. It is a recyclable TPV that processes like a thermoplastic and acts like rubber. It is used in films, skins, foils, body seals, weatherstripping, hoses, tubes, and profile extrusion. This product is suitable for Extrusion.

 

Applications:


Large components
Appliances
Automotive Interior Trim
Boat
Jet-propelled Vehicle


 


Features:


Airbag Covers
Interior Trim
Handle Grips


 


Benefits:


Excellent Low Temperature Ductility
